Introduction
============
Here you find a few tools to debug and test the mcproxy.


Create tap devices
==================
An easy way to test the mcproxy without physical hardware is 
to create tap devices.

Compilation
-----------
Build create_tap_device:

    cd create_tap_device
    qmake
    make

Usage
-----
Create a tap device

    sudo ./tap.sh create tap_name add 192.168.33.1 netmask 255.255.255.255

Delete a tap device

    sudo ./tap.sh delete tap_name
